  "body": "**Is your feature request related to a problem? Please describe.**\r\n\r\nIs RocksDb currently version 7.7.3, however 7.8.0+ reduces [write amplification](https://rocksdb.org/blog/2022/10/31/align-compaction-output-file.html) for added performance\r\n\r\n**Describe the solution you'd like**\r\n\r\nUpgrade RocksDb to a version after 7.8.0\r\n\r\n**Describe alternatives you've considered**\r\n\r\nAlterative storage mechanisms (incompatible upgrade, more difficult evaluation); alternative storage structure to reduce read/writes (complex)\r\n\r\n**Additional context**\r\n\r\nBlog post from RockDb team from [Reduce Write Amplification by Aligning Compaction Output File Boundaries](https://rocksdb.org/blog/2022/10/31/align-compaction-output-file.html) October 31, 2022",
